description:
A Hand-drawn 10x8 inch Canvas by me with the word of your choice.

Whether its a Birthday present or a treat, you will be presented with a high quality canvas.

Comes with free stickers.

Email me the information for the canvas at: amossstickerart@gmail.com

Required information is:

-Word (Any particular style?)
-Lettering Colour
-Message on Back (Optional)
-Sprayed Background (If wanted)
